      "text_span_id": "results_1",
      "text": "The mean knowledge, attitude, and practice scores were 9.39 \u00b1 3.82 (possible range: 0\u201320), 31.4 \u00b1 4.06 (possible range: 8\u201340), and 25.2 \u00b1 7.04 (possible range: 8\u201340), respectively.",
